www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/most-beloved-best-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":40829,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The Prophet&#8217;s beloved have best character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I tell you about the most beloved to me and the closest to my assembly on the Day of Resurrection? Those with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 272 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/bad-neighbors-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40829,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: How many bad neighbors on Judgment Day?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHow many neighbors will be brought with their neighbors on the Day of Resurrection? One will say: O Lord, this man closed his door to me and refused to show courtesy!\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 111\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42704,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/07\/mercy-even-to-birds\/","url_m